"""
PART II Entitlement and amount

6. Amount of the guarantee credit

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-31.

(5) The additional amount applicable is—
(b) £163.00 per week if paragraph 1(1)(b) of Part I of Schedule I is satisfied otherwise than by virtue of paragraph 1(2)(b) of that Part and no one is entitled to and in receipt of an allowance under section 70 of the 1992 Act or carer support payment, or has an award of universal credit which includes the carer element under regulation 29 of the Universal Credit Regulations 2013, in respect of caring for either partner.
"""

pc_schedule1_part1_paragraph1_1_b_satisfied_other_than_by_paragraph1_2_b:
    entity: TaxUnit
    period: Week
    dtype: Boolean

pc_no_one_gets_carer_allowance_carer_support_payment_or_uc_carer_element_for_either_partner:
    entity: TaxUnit
    period: Week
    dtype: Boolean

pc_severe_disability_addition_two_eligible_adults_weekly_rate:
    entity: TaxUnit
    period: Week
    dtype: Money
    unit: GBP
    from 2025-03-31:
        if pc_schedule1_part1_paragraph1_1_b_satisfied_other_than_by_paragraph1_2_b and pc_no_one_gets_carer_allowance_carer_support_payment_or_uc_carer_element_for_either_partner:
            163.00
        else:
            0
